Hey there. I just got a new laptop and I am trying to run driver station on it and I keep getting this error.

image902×550 11.9 KB

I suspect it’s because my cpu is the Snapdragon X plus but I’m not sure if there is any way to fix this. Any help is greatly appreciated!

The Snapdragon X Plus is an ARM CPU, which is not compatible with x86 programs like the driver station unfortunately. Windows can emulate x86 programs on ARM but the driver station in particular has SSE/SSE2 instructions which I assume can’t be emulated.

It’s actually a bug in the LabVIEW code for the DS. There are internal builds that are fixed, but the fix didn’t make it into the 2025 DS.
